== Overview ==
The Crusader class bot is a self sufficient standalone class of bot. Although the turret can hold only one weapon, it is designed to maximize damage and accuracy, every shot fired is the equivalent to a critical hit. The Crusader also boasts four shield slots and heavy armor, making it possibly the most durable bot after the [[Leviathan]].

Sells for 120192 credits.

